---
title: Honey-Sumac Prawns & Couscous Salad with Garlic Dip & Hazelnuts
description: The couscous is so fluffy that it’s cuddling the fresh prawns in a warm hug! Let those flavours embrace you with sumac
seasoning and honey, all pulled together with crunchy roasted almonds and a garlicky dip.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
